    pulse

    pulse.problem.statements
    Introduces various problem statements for the heat conduction problem in the laser flash experiment.
    pulse.ui.charts
    A package that is responsible for (a) plotting charts to display and interact with data from HeatingCurve objects; and (b) plotting preview charts from ResultTables.
